
Hardware:

* Some component values are subject to change to adjust MPP range and output
  voltage

* Handle bias voltage of OP-AMP.

* Schematic has undergone some changes that didn't go in the PCB yet.

* Current design is for  VRLA 12 V battery

Software:

* Make communication via serial port bidirectional

* Make certain settings configurable via serial

* Send data from MPPT to the router only on demand

* Add sleep states

